# https://hargitai.co.nz/xcode-cant-update-install-from-mac-appstore-is-stuck-on-waiting/


```The connection to ACDAccountStore was invalidated```
Close the AppStore.app
In a terminal: killall appstoreagent
Open  ~/Library/Caches/
Delete the com.apple.appstore folder
Open /private/var/folders
Search all of the subfolders and delete all instances of com.apple.appstore
Restart your Mac
